section.para:
   If you want to extend or edit this list, switch to the config/ directory and open the
   crawler-user-agents.json file with the editor of your choice. The content can look like this:

   [
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot\\/",
       "url": "http://www.google.com/bot.html"
   },
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot-Mobile"
   },
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot-Image"
   },
   [...]
]

  Let's assume we want to add the bot Geekobot to the list of bots and the user agent looks like this:
  Mozilla/5.0 (compatible; Geekobot/2.1; +https://www.opensuse.org)
  Our unique part would be Geekobot. So we add a new entry to the list of bots:
  [
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot\\/",
       "url": "http://www.google.com/bot.html"
   },
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot-Mobile"
   },
   {
       "pattern": "Googlebot-Image"
   },
   [...]
   {
       "pattern": "Geekobot"
   }
]
